                                    <br>

                                    <ol class="event-details__inner__list">
                                        <li>
                                            <p>
                                                Advice for Aspiring Non-Profit Founders: <br>
                                                Young people looking to start non-profits in Germany should have clear
                                                visions and goals, and focus on long-term sustainability to avoid
                                                short-lived initiatives. For guidance on registering an e.V., visit:
                                                https://deutsches-ehrenamt.de/vereinsgruendung-vereinsarten/vereinsgruendung/
                                                (this is just an example website for step to step guide and it might be
                                                different for different regions and states)

                                            </p>
                                        </li>
                                        <li>
                                            <p>
                                                Challenge of Team Retention: <br>
                                                Maintaining motivation among team members is a major challenge. It's
                                                common for only a few dedicated individuals to remain active, while
                                                others may leave for various reasons.

                                            </p>
                                        </li>
                                        <li>
                                            <p>
                                                Task Allocation in Nepali Samaj e.V. Based on Expertise: <br>
                                                Within Nepali Samaj e.V., team members are assigned responsibilities
                                                according to their skills, such as handling cultural initiatives, IT
                                                management, and social media operations, ensuring efficient operations.

                                            </p>
                                        </li>
                                        <li>
                                            <p>
                                                Promoting Cultural Integration through Nepali Samaj e.V.: <br>
                                                Significant impact has been made by Nepali Samaj e.V. in promoting
                                                Nepali culture and traditions, not just within the Nepali community but
                                                also among local Germans, fostering greater understanding and inclusion.

                                            </p>
                                        </li>

                                        <li>
                                            <p>
                                                Successful Projects in Nepal by Nepali Samaj e.V.:<br>
                                                Besides cultural work in Germany, Nepali Samaj e.V. has executed
                                                impactful projects in Nepal, contributing to social and developmental
                                                causes in both countries.


                                            </p>
                                        </li>

                                        <li>
                                            <p>
                                                Inclusion of Local Germans:<br>
                                                Integrating local Germans and people frm other Nationalities into the
                                                mission is essential. Avoid creating isolated communities and instead
                                                focus on familiarizing locals with the organizationâ€™s cultural goals and
