                                                non-profit sector is crucial for expanding outreach and ensuring
                                                sustained impact.
                                            </p>
                                        </li>

                                        <li>
                                            <p>
                                                Financial Transparency through Auditing:<br>
                                                Financial transparency is ensured by conducting regular audits, although
                                                the organization (as an e.V.) is only required to share financial
                                                details with its members.

                                            </p>
                                        </li>


                                        <li>
