                                                Continuously working towards organizational goals builds support for
                                                projects. Useful resources for funding and support include: <br>
                                                https://www.stifter-helfen.de/ <br>
                                                https://www.bamf.de/ <br>
                                                https://www.bmz.de/en

                                            </p>
                                        </li>


                                        <li>
