                                                other similar organizations (e.V.s) in Germany by creating an umbrella
                                                structure to unify efforts. This will enhance collaboration, resource
                                                sharing, and a collective impact on both the German and Nepali
                                                communities. Encouraging individuals and organizations in Germany to
                                                actively support and engage with this mission will further expand the
                                                scope of the work.
                                            </p>
